<br>
Might have been in a Negative way as well.. You might have been out playing soccer one day, instead of sitting in front of the Computer, and caught a stay bullet that left you paralyzed from the neck down. You will never know what will happen until it does. God (whichever one you chose to believe in) grants you a certain amount of time on Earth, what you CHOOSE to do with that time is yours. <br>
<br>
Yes without the game your life would be different and could very well be in a more positive way, but you will never know now.<br>
<br>
